      "review_summary": "This PR replaces direct JSON success-response parsing with file-local 1 MiB `readResponseWithLimit` wrappers across Feishu, Browser, MS Teams, Azure Speech, Bedrock Mantle, Google Chat, HuggingFace, and Perplexity, plus proof tests/scripts.\n\nPR surface: Source +123, Tests +233. Total +356 across 18 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source: current main still has direct `response.json()`/`res.json()` success reads in several touched modules, while sibling paths already use bounded provider JSON helpers. I did not run a live oversized-response repro in this read-only review.",
